Subject: Our Adventures into Indie Games or 'Mistakes Were Made'
Description: Mahjong House was the first commercial video game from DisjointedImages. Come listen to how we developed the game, how it was a success (and failure), and get some tips on venturing into the world of indie game development yourself.  Speakers include:Melanie Castle, Chris Castle - Track: Tech, Videogaming  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
